{"tid":748951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人點睇拍拖?","createTime":"2018-07-19T15:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T05:35:44.000Z","uid":187524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4e929d177ff5e3d023e8bc2db6afc382fdb89cac","tid":748951,"uid":187524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"真係好矛盾<br />\n多數屋企人會叫你讀書果時唔好拍拖<br />\n等出嚟做嘢先拍<br />\n我真係好奇出嚟做嘢可以點拍拖<br />\n正常讀完書都已經22<br />\n當你頭一兩年專心做嘢<br />\n已經24<br />\n24歲人A0無拍拖經驗<br />\n假設身邊咁啱都有差唔多大嘅女都係A0就無問題姐<br />\n但事實係而家邊有咁多20幾歲女仲係A0<br />\n自問而家拍拖無影響讀書<br />\n唔明點解屋企人會反對拍拖<br />\n當儲下經驗都好<br />\n求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎大家分享自己睇法"},{"pid":"83f30786beaf4df7960193af22cbdd7bd5056552","tid":748951,"uid":117947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"女朋友係國家分配架<br />\n唔洗特登去拍拖"},{"pid":"6b21e2b88767d8c364a16ec6d34be31342144a4b","tid":748951,"uid":187524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f30786beaf4df7960193af22cbdd7bd5056552","tid":748951,"uid":117947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:25:44.000Z","msg":"女朋友係國家分配架<br />\n唔洗特登去拍拖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:31:03.000Z","msg":"咁你慢慢等下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb09a07fb3fd9ae884d00245f4335479839b30d5","tid":748951,"uid":89608,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"瞞住屋企人是常識吧"},{"pid":"f9d42b33920a9192b326c682772fd1be91d7949d","tid":748951,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b21e2b88767d8c364a16ec6d34be31342144a4b","tid":748951,"uid":187524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f30786